What you need to know:  Chelsea, who are in Premier League action against Norwich later on Thursday, have been given a special licence to continue to operateCaptain Cesar Azpilicueta and key defender Antonio Rudiger, among those out of contract at the end of the season, could leave on a free transferSeason-ticket holders at Stamford Bridge will be allowed to attend matches, but no ticket or merchandise sales that would mean funds going to the club are permitted